{"tid":786321,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"(花生) 大地主慘被撚狗精華","createTime":"2018-08-19T23:53:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-26T04:14:37.000Z","uid":17866,"like":34,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"580a8642a549ac687bc53aa19a8a21883c1cc609","tid":786321,"uid":17866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T23:53:10.000Z","msg":"分享下低智區大地主山林道 被撚至崩潰妄想症病發實錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n事源:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/779633/page/12\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/779633/page/12</a><br />\n<br />\n當大家討論緊QE完縮表同其他經濟因素對來緊樓價咩影響時, 當然唔少得低智區一眾人士入去引戰, 之後大佬出場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#293開始<br />\n<br />\n大地主一入場已自我感覺良好, 個個想做佢佢租租 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/18/000754_468515012b3e45eb9179ba6f2778a74c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F18%2F000754_468515012b3e45eb9179ba6f2778a74c.jpg&h=41f365c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n低智區名言: &quot;有錢你唔上車咩, 你地班窮撚無錢先唔上&quot;  被小弟係另一個POST應一眾低智區業主貼下STATEMENT破解左, 山林道為首一眾低智區業主因大絕被破而龍顏大怒, 係搵唔到可以人身攻擊既地方下,  佢地作出一個經典既痴線案例:  幻想虛構對方有著悲慘背景, 並就幻想內容進行恥笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 精神勝利法既極限表現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家睇下佢開始幻想到o的咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n無故幻想對方係SALES要見客,生活好慘又係FG, 又香港大把人30歲前單人上車, 又炒股輸左身家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 更多不能盡錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/18/001617_050d44b6f783fee3526949d5facd3fde.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F18%2F001617_050d44b6f783fee3526949d5facd3fde.jpg&h=4f23f3c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/18/012814_f0bbbae763276a4eef018e7b51c81467.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F18%2F012814_f0bbbae763276a4eef018e7b51c81467.jpg&h=37605565&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/18/012815_9c8b709f9ee7f1678a747c23f6085db2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F18%2F012815_9c8b709f9ee7f1678a747c23f6085db2.jpg&h=59904796&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/18/012815_66c46e9fdc64b1a53bb2217d46fb1657.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F18%2F012815_66c46e9fdc64b1a53bb2217d46fb1657.jpg&h=b96581ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/18/012815_336c1913654154c81dcf75feee46b823.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F18%2F012815_336c1913654154c81dcf75feee46b823.jpg&h=b5ac99dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/18/012816_667436e0410fa36c0a16bbbecb805a0f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F18%2F012816_667436e0410fa36c0a16bbbecb805a0f.jpg&h=b0a97880&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/18/012816_d1d0a6338180916addabc3363f629c32.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F18%2F012816_d1d0a6338180916addabc3363f629c32.jpg&h=e23f6b0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/18/013326_f3cacb89efb9893460624e1599883bf4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F18%2F013326_f3cacb89efb9893460624e1599883bf4.jpg&h=a6ac1975&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/19/230852_655172a414f6c8cf25e5d55b6c64c2c0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F19%2F230852_655172a414f6c8cf25e5d55b6c64c2c0.jpg&h=631bc943&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔知點解好鐘意叫 [2球] ,連個source係佢院友們自己係度叫出來都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n幻想內容簡介:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/18/013244_62861bdc97cd83dc110cc8018cace5de.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F18%2F013244_62861bdc97cd83dc110cc8018cace5de.jpg&h=272bf165&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n戲肉黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我問佢幻想我係sales, 如果唔係點呢? 有人笠水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/18/013625_e77b252ea55500b3d8a2c1502e7c9023.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F18%2F013625_e77b252ea55500b3d8a2c1502e7c9023.jpg&h=7bb23469&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/19/231525_8491f70f0954b89d2752f233ac9e0c54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F19%2F231525_8491f70f0954b89d2752f233ac9e0c54.jpg&h=9889858e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/18/013828_6d81b1f715a690c1207c079d91e689f6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F18%2F013828_6d81b1f715a690c1207c079d91e689f6.jpg&h=0dc7e04b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n山林boy回覆: <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/18/014129_5310782b3b85f1e6d2e1efe2af7ca2bc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F18%2F014129_5310782b3b85f1e6d2e1efe2af7ca2bc.jpg&h=2857bff1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/18/014704_032296a40a1992e365ee92b6f81a1a99.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F18%2F014704_032296a40a1992e365ee92b6f81a1a99.jpg&h=ff40b50d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔敢對質, 又再妄想發作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一個下午突然之間樓價突破天際, 2.6球上唔到車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  之後對方仲突然輸左身家,身無分文<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後被問至駁唔到, 開始前言不對後語,語無倫次<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/18/014410_7f9d46d7260d149b0119a52d89cdf33a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F18%2F014410_7f9d46d7260d149b0119a52d89cdf33a.jpg&h=c8ef0320&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係早幾格既回覆證明佢關心到人地成個背景記曬加幻想左人地半生事績 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/18/014444_1b56cc7e6bc24ed1469a43fd06682016.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F18%2F014444_1b56cc7e6bc24ed1469a43fd06682016.jpg&h=a599514d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不能分類柒事:<br />\n文盲, 當字都唔識解 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/19/230541_1814ac8a25a527bf98a5d090ad1d49e4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F19%2F230541_1814ac8a25a527bf98a5d090ad1d49e4.jpg&h=8c5fbeb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聲稱自己收租過活, 毫無社會工作常識, 鄉下仔笑城市人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連大部分公司有INTERNET POLICY同MON機常識都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/19/231047_60ea5cd54c20f8f747c90ad874231dc7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F19%2F231047_60ea5cd54c20f8f747c90ad874231dc7.jpg&h=9416f060&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/19/231101_9669ef2574043a47aaed68652d4af2bc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F19%2F231101_9669ef2574043a47aaed68652d4af2bc.jpg&h=95e677f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來識開機閂機就叫有電腦工作知識 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/19/231130_8585d948fb4d6166dd4e925017c704b0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F19%2F231130_8585d948fb4d6166dd4e925017c704b0.jpg&h=d63d35f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被人駁到無聲出又唔敢對質怕柒, <br />\n最後堂堂暴發戶大帝被佢口中既[廢淡] 撚至情緒崩潰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 開始發爛炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/19/232542_7e27384adde28ecfec14fd47ab99bed5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F19%2F232542_7e27384adde28ecfec14fd47ab99bed5.jpg&h=bf58f486&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/19/232544_d48fb031529ee79f33af1b2d158dd3b7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F19%2F232544_d48fb031529ee79f33af1b2d158dd3b7.jpg&h=f5bfbd01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n往後既內容都係無內容, 所以用呢張圖簡介<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/c/cb/Tramuncle.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20070408093619\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2Fc%2Fcb%2FTramuncle.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20070408093619&h=5fa5cf7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n完<br />\n========================================<br />\n<br />\n後記: 近2個POST既對答後發現低智區人士對所有非唱好言論者會做既並唔係講道理或者經濟理論, 而係會聯群人身攻擊加抹黑對方.  唔係由道理上說服達至[嬴], 而係透過抹黑對方令對方不可信而[輸]<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> .<br />\n<br />\n此技量甚沒營養, 一但對方無視挑釁,據理解釋可輕易應付<br />\n<br />\n而令人驚訝既係佢地當發現 &quot;有錢你唔會上車咩,死窮撚&quot; 同埋抹黑無效後,佢地竟然會幻想對方背景悲慘, 並以佢地自行幻想既內容進行攻擊同恥笑. <br />\n呢種行為發生一人身上不出奇,但低智區業主可以一班人集體催眠自己再集體單方面宣佈己方勝利並恥笑對方精神勝利, 精神健康情況令人擔憂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後, 我已經達致令低智區顛狗醜態盡露<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 既目的, 留番既就等大家食花生開心下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  等佢地入來表演&quot;屌爆你個閪呀&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  多謝收睇"},{"pid":"dd1f9169798a27f8fc42eeae4c9a03561e881f01","tid":786321,"uid":60219,"like":54,"dislike":14,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T00:01:34.000Z","msg":"你人生咁短暫，但你偏偏用咁多時間做埋d無謂嘢，上咁耐連登cap咁多圖浪費曬d可以增值自己嘅寶貴時間，竟然仲要係到自我感覺良好<br />\n<br />\n你唔覺得你自己好可悲咩"},{"pid":"bff3c6da4fa54dfd60181e7dd547a7c4fabbf300","tid":786321,"uid":22422,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T00:04:24.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"74476c8a6ff041744f8de45468d70225372377f0","tid":786321,"uid":17866,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T00:06:28.000Z","msg":"悶嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搵野磨下時間"},{"pid":"757bf12c4ed4c845273d31e680dbab0bbc8c0eda","tid":786321,"uid":84771,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T00:07:03.000Z","msg":"劏房業主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb5910433011ef32f427cf3a264953ca5a1e48cc","tid":786321,"uid":186692,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T00:21:33.000Z","msg":"啲賤種唔肯死喺個閪post入面自己圍爐<br />\n係要出嚟擺款笑柒人拎存在感"},{"pid":"f28158a22e48d4d0a9e81db23c782d6f3254b6cf","tid":786321,"uid":17866,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T01:12:35.000Z","msg":"山林道地主縮埋番去圍爐區唔出現喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪圖文並茂駁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n邀請你出黎再發表下偉論<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"616fca54d79c0981332cf96fcf58ff66f3ed122a","tid":786321,"uid":17866,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T01:13:49.000Z","msg":"其他日日賺，put乜，柒鵰大大聲個班唔出黎護主既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4116242c860c99fdad1dd1884879cb812153df5b","tid":786321,"uid":122377,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T03:31:46.000Z","msg":"支持樓主 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主好人 一生平安 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"814df0f8a2a3894efd60edcf9c5f709461b45445","tid":786321,"uid":122377,"like":14,"dislike":3,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"f2